### **1.6 Security & Visitor Administration (/education/admin/security) <span style="color:red">(NEW)</span>**
**Visitor Management Executive Dashboard** (/education/admin/security/dashboard)
**Color Scheme:** Security Blue with alert Red accents
**Access Level:** Security staff, School administration, Front desk personnel
**Content Structure:**
**Visitor Analytics:**
*   Daily/Monthly Visitor Volume by Inviter Role
*   Visitor Type Distribution (Parents, Contractors, Guests)
*   Average Visit Duration by Department
*   Pending Approval Requests by Inviter
*   Overstay Alerts & Violations with Inviter Accountability
**Security Operations:**
*   Active Visitors on Campus with Inviter Information
*   Scheduled Visits for Today with Host Details
*   Pending Background Checks for Contractors
*   Security Checkpoint Status
**Compliance Monitoring:**
*   Visitor Policy Compliance Rates by Inviter
*   Emergency Evacuation Readiness
*   Access Control Violations with Inviter Tracking
*   Incident Reporting Status
* * *
## **Visitor Management Modules**
### **1.6.1 Multi-Role Visitor Invite System (/education/admin/security/visitor-invite) <span style="color:red">(NEW)</span>**
**Enhanced Invitation Workflow:**
*       *   **Multi-Role Invitation Initiation:Administrators:** Full invitation privileges for any visitor type
    *   **Teachers:** Parent meetings, guest speakers, classroom volunteers
    *   **Students:** Parent/guardian visits (requires teacher approval)
    *   **Staff:** Contractors, service providers, vendors
    *   **Approval Process with Inviter Tracking:**Management receives requests with complete inviter details
    *   Background check integration linked to inviter responsibility
    *   Approval chain shows inviter → approver hierarchy
    *   Automated approval based on inviter authority level
    *   **Smart QR Code Generation:**Embedded inviter information in QR data structure
    *   Role-based access permissions derived from inviter
    *   Escalation contacts based on inviter department
    *   Inviter notification upon visitor arrival/departure
**Integration Points:** Teacher portals, Parent portals, Student portals, Staff scheduling systems
### **1.6.2 Enhanced Visitor Check-in System (/education/admin/security/checkin) <span style="color:red">(NEW)</span>**
**Check-in Process with Inviter Verification:**
*   QR code scanning displays visitor + inviter information
*   Photo capture and customized badge printing
*   Emergency contact verification with inviter backup
*   Purpose of visit confirmation against inviter's schedule
**Enhanced Safety Features:**
*   Sex Offender Registry cross-check
*   Custody restriction alerts with inviter notification
*   Visitor blacklist screening
*   COVID-19 screening questionnaire
**Inviter-Focused Reminder System:** Pre-visit notifications to both visitor and inviter, Host alerts, Check-in confirmations
### **1.6.3 Visitor Monitoring & Overstay Management (/education/admin/security/monitoring) <span style="color:red">(NEW)</span>**
**Real-time Monitoring with Inviter Accountability:**
*   Active visitor dashboard showing visitor location + inviter details
*   Visit duration tracking with inviter responsibility
*   Automatic check-out reminders to visitor AND inviter
*   Host notification system with escalation to inviter's manager
**Enhanced Overstay Detection:**
*   Automated flagging for exceeded stay duration
*   Escalation protocols: Visitor → Inviter → Department Head → Security
*   Security alert generation with inviter contact information
*   Management notification system with inviter performance tracking
**Inviter-Based Response Procedures:**
*   Tier 1 (15 min before end): Notify Visitor + Inviter
*   Tier 2 (30 min overdue): Notify Inviter + Security
*   Tier 3 (60+ min overdue): Notify Inviter's Manager + Full Security
*   Tier 4 (90+ min): Emergency protocols activation
### **1.6.4 Emergency & Incident Management (/education/admin/security/emergency) <span style="color:red">(NEW)</span>**
**Enhanced Emergency Features:**
*   Instant campus-wide visitor roll call with inviter contacts
*   Emergency evacuation tracking by inviter responsibility
*   Lockdown procedure integration with inviter accountability
*   Real-time visitor location mapping with inviter information
**Incident Reporting with Inviter Chain:**
*   Security incident documentation linked to inviter
*   Visitor violation tracking by inviter department
*   Follow-up action management assigned to inviter
*   Compliance reporting with inviter performance metrics

