# 4\. Hospitality Vertical — Complete Portal Ecosystem
* * *
## 4.0 Cross‑Vertical Foundation (Core System)
### Unified Visitor & Access Management Engine
A shared system powering all portals.
**Core Capabilities**
*   Central Visitor Registry (single source of truth)
*   QR code & access code generation
*   Time‑bound, recurring, and permanent visitor access
*   Approval workflows (Guest ↔ Staff ↔ Security)
*   Visitor monetization (paid visits, consultations, events)
*   Attendance tracking & analytics
*   Visitor limits & access enforcement
*   Event credit system (food, drinks, services)
**Shared Entities**
*   Guest
*   Visitor
*   Visit Session
*   Event
*   Credit Wallet
*   Property / Room / Estate
* * *
