*   Check‑in & check‑out times
*   Digital key (if applicable)
*   Real‑time folio & billing
*   Booked services (spa, dining, transport)
*   Events
#### Visitor Overview
*   Total visitors invited
*   Pending vs approved visitors
*   Visitor limit usage (e.g. 5 / 10)
